query:
SELECT 
  ti.id as invitation_id,
  ti.employeeId,
  ti.status as invitation_status,
  ti.testType,
  ti.completedAt as invitation_completed,
  tr.id as result_id,
  tr.completedAt as result_completed,
  e.email,
  e.name
FROM testInvitations ti
LEFT JOIN employees e ON ti.employeeId = e.id
LEFT JOIN testResults tr ON tr.invitationId = ti.id
WHERE e.email = 'rodrigo.goncalves@uisa.com.br'
ORDER BY ti.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
